The paper proposes a visual language for querying complex-value databases, which falls under the category of database systems (cs.DB). The language also involves a design metaphor, which could be related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the expressive power of the language, which could be related to software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper emphasizes the intuitive design of the language, which could be related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
